keyMappings:
unmapAll

# local navigation
map h scrollLeft
map j scrollDown
map k scrollUp
map l scrollRight
map gg scrollToTop
map G scrollToBottom
map <c-f> scrollPageDown
map <c-b> scrollPageUp
map 0 scrollToLeft
map $ scrollToRight

map gf nextFrame
map gF mainFrame
map m Marks.activateCreateMode
map ' Marks.activateGotoMode

# modes
map i enterInsertMode
map v enterVisualMode
map e enterVisualLineMode
map gi focusInput
map f LinkHints.activateMode
map F LinkHints.activateModeToOpenInNewTab
map U LinkHints.activateModeToDownloadLink

# find mode
map / enterFindMode
map n performFind
map N performBackwardsFind

# tab management
map <c-t> createTab
map gT previousTab
map gt nextTab
map g0 firstTab
map g$ lastTab
map <c-T> restoreTab
map <c-w> removeTab

map <c-r> reload
map <c-m> toggleMuteTab

# external navigation
map yy copyCurrentUrl
map P openCopiedUrlInNewTab
map <c-e> Vomnibar.activateEditUrl
map <c-E> Vomnibar.activateEditUrlInNewTab
